==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Pelter
<hw>Pel"ter</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A pinchpenny; a mean,
sordid person; a miser; a skinflint.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
⟦ldquo⟧Let such <xex>pelters</xex> prate.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Gascoigne.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

